      "passCount": {
        "min": 1,
        "max": 10,
        "value": 2,
        "unit": "passes",
        "description": "Multi-pass (2 recommended) for complete removal of heavy contaminants without single-pass overload on delicate GaN; single pass for light. Based on industrial practice for semiconductors. Source: Case studies in Surf. Coat. Technol. 2019."
